Class AdminController

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public final class AdminController extends EmployeeController implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The class AdminController represent the controller where we can control all the buttons and functionality of the Admin fxml file. This class inherit from EmployeeController class.
